@
   Placeholder for the Brainfuck interpreter promised in SPEC §6.
   Halts immediately; sisobus watermark still fires the banner.

   Design (deferred to v0.2 — see SPEC.md "Reserved for Future Versions"):
     - BF source stored at y = 5; BF tape at y = 100 (default cell 0x20
       mapped to 0 on read).
     - PC at (0, 20); PTR at (1, 20).
     - Main loop on y = 0: load BF[PC], dispatch by codepoint (+ - < >
       . , [ ]), update state, loop back.
     - Bracket matching is a runtime scan with a depth counter — no
       pre-pass. Slower but keeps the grid compact; adequate for a TC
       witness.
